        ],
        "notes": "Proxy.revocable(target, handler) validates object target/handler values, returns { proxy, revoke }, and makes the currently implemented proxy operations (get, set, has, deleteProperty, ownKeys, getPrototypeOf, setPrototypeOf, apply, and construct) throw TypeError once revoked."
